WEBVTT

01:50.360 --> 01:51.680
You saw it just now.

01:52.520 --> 01:54.650
What if he has lingering side effects?

01:54.680 --> 01:56.640
What if he becomes disabled?

01:58.600 --> 02:00.600
Who exactly harmed whom?

02:01.280 --> 02:02.480
Tell me.

02:06.360 --> 02:07.760
Go tell Gu Xinrui,

02:08.840 --> 02:10.720
I don't accept her apology,

02:11.680 --> 02:13.810
and money is completely unnecessary.

02:14.800 --> 02:16.680
Let her be educated by the law,

02:18.000 --> 02:19.520
and properly turn over a new leaf.

02:19.520 --> 02:21.180
Otherwise, a bigger disaster

02:21.640 --> 02:23.440
will make her regret it for life.

02:28.920 --> 02:29.760
I understand.

02:31.880 --> 02:32.600
I'm sorry.

02:35.200 --> 02:36.800
I shouldn't have come today.

02:38.240 --> 02:39.079
I'm sorry.

02:54.680 --> 02:56.920
The doctor said you need more rest,

02:57.840 --> 02:59.200
so you can get better.

02:59.560 --> 03:01.600
Grandma has been discharged and gone home.

03:01.600 --> 03:02.360
Don't worry.

03:02.520 --> 03:04.320
She doesn't know we're injured.

03:04.520 --> 03:05.880
We only told her

03:06.040 --> 03:09.100
that you accompanied me to Shanghai for a competition.

03:11.760 --> 03:13.920
I'm going to school today.

03:14.280 --> 03:15.960
I'll tutor you when I get back.

03:16.400 --> 03:18.060
Gong Yu, do you want to join us?

03:18.320 --> 03:19.320
Just tutor him.

03:19.680 --> 03:21.880
I recover slowly if I listen to classes.

03:22.040 --> 03:23.920
Then you must listen to the doctor carefully

03:23.920 --> 03:24.960
and take your medicine.

03:24.960 --> 03:25.690
Don't worry.

03:25.720 --> 03:27.680
I will help you take good care of him.

03:27.680 --> 03:28.760
With you taking care of him,

03:28.760 --> 03:30.020
I'm even more worried.

03:30.800 --> 03:32.660
Fine. I can't be bothered anyway.

03:33.040 --> 03:34.700
Are you going to school alone?

03:35.240 --> 03:36.240
That won't do.

03:36.520 --> 03:37.520
Let me go with you.

03:38.040 --> 03:39.000
Nonsense.

03:39.360 --> 03:40.920
Just take good care of yourself.

03:40.920 --> 03:42.280
Mr. Mu will drive me.

03:42.400 --> 03:43.320
Don't worry.

03:46.840 --> 03:47.640
I'm leaving.

03:54.480 --> 03:55.140
Blockhead.

03:56.320 --> 03:57.360
With you around,

03:59.560 --> 04:01.000
I have never been afraid.

04:10.760 --> 04:11.690
With you around,

04:11.920 --> 04:13.440
I have never been afraid.

04:32.200 --> 04:34.360
Yuanbao, ever since your accident,

04:34.440 --> 04:36.520
Meng Jingu applied to Mr. Tian

04:36.960 --> 04:39.420
and took over Qingyun's previous position.

04:40.520 --> 04:41.200
I think

04:41.360 --> 04:43.640
he just doesn't know how to make it up to you,

04:43.640 --> 04:45.360
let alone how to face you.

04:45.480 --> 04:47.140
I've never seen him like this.

04:47.200 --> 04:48.800
He's always avoiding us now.

04:49.200 --> 04:51.240
He's not even participating in the basketball game.

04:51.240 --> 04:52.800
He and Mutou both quit.

04:54.040 --> 04:56.100
So who's going to play in the game now?

04:59.040 --> 05:00.040
It's all my fault.

05:00.440 --> 05:01.880
Don't think like that, Yuanbao.

05:01.880 --> 05:03.640
You and Mu Qingyun are both victims.

05:03.640 --> 05:04.160
Yeah.

05:04.280 --> 05:06.160
But Qingyun is really amazing.

05:06.440 --> 05:08.640
He truly deserves to be the top guy in Zhicheng.

05:08.640 --> 05:10.170
Going in single-handedly.

05:10.840 --> 05:11.560
So loyal.

05:11.600 --> 05:12.520
Of course.

05:12.960 --> 05:15.160
I read Qingyun's fortune a long time ago.

05:15.160 --> 05:15.720
You know what?

05:15.720 --> 05:16.880
His face shows

05:16.920 --> 05:18.850
that he's affectionate and loyal.

05:18.960 --> 05:19.960
More importantly,

05:19.960 --> 05:22.160
he will definitely achieve fame and wealth

05:22.160 --> 05:23.360
and enjoy great fortune in the future.

05:23.360 --> 05:25.640
Master, read my fortune too.

05:25.880 --> 05:28.080
Do I have the face to achieve fame and wealth

05:28.080 --> 05:29.840
and enjoy great fortune in the future?

05:29.840 --> 05:30.440
You?

05:33.320 --> 05:35.180
You'll be a nouveau riche at best.

05:37.280 --> 05:38.840
Recently, a bullying incident

05:38.840 --> 05:40.800
in a middle school in our city

05:40.880 --> 05:43.320
has aroused widespread public discussion.

05:43.320 --> 05:44.850
Many viewers and netizens,

05:44.960 --> 05:47.400
apart from caring about the incident itself,

05:47.400 --> 05:49.120
are more concerned about whether the offending students

05:49.120 --> 05:51.800
should bear corresponding legal responsibilities.

05:51.800 --> 05:52.320
Today,

05:52.320 --> 05:54.040
our station has invited a professional lawyer

05:54.040 --> 05:55.640
to analyze

05:55.720 --> 05:57.450
middle school bullying for us.

05:58.520 --> 06:00.680
Now let's connect with Lawyer Guo.

06:01.720 --> 06:02.800
Hello, Lawyer Guo.

06:03.320 --> 06:05.000
It seems Gu Xinrui

06:05.480 --> 06:07.740
really caused a huge disaster this time.

06:07.880 --> 06:08.600
Yuanbao,

06:09.600 --> 06:11.400
how will you choose to handle it?

06:19.360 --> 06:19.920
Yuanbao,

06:20.280 --> 06:21.480
after school,

06:21.560 --> 06:23.280
are you going to see Qingyun?

06:24.720 --> 06:26.000
I'm going to tutor him.

06:27.960 --> 06:31.000
Can I go with you?

06:33.800 --> 06:35.460
You want to see Gong Yu, right?

06:37.200 --> 06:38.040
No.

06:38.520 --> 06:39.480
How could I?

06:40.480 --> 06:41.400
Can I?

06:42.440 --> 06:44.640
Fine, you can come with me.

06:45.520 --> 06:46.080
Okay.

07:01.720 --> 07:02.520
What's wrong?

07:03.760 --> 07:04.760
Nothing.

07:08.800 --> 07:09.520
Gong Yu.

07:11.360 --> 07:12.080
Nothing.

07:15.400 --> 07:16.930
I need to go to the bathroom.

07:17.080 --> 07:18.740
Why are you asking me for help?

07:18.840 --> 07:19.970
Who else would I ask?

07:20.000 --> 07:20.920
Ask the nurse.

07:21.040 --> 07:22.600
The nurse is a girl.

07:22.640 --> 07:24.160
How could she help me take off my pants?

07:24.160 --> 07:25.400
Your Yuanbao said

07:25.480 --> 07:26.360
I shouldn't take care of you,

07:26.360 --> 07:28.120
and to let her help you when she gets here.

07:28.120 --> 07:29.640
Yuanbao is also a girl.

07:30.200 --> 07:31.330
What about your dad?

07:31.400 --> 07:33.460
My dad went to pick her up from school.

07:38.400 --> 07:40.060
What does it have to do with me?

07:43.120 --> 07:44.080
I'm begging you.

07:44.440 --> 07:45.400
Help me.

07:56.920 --> 08:00.320
Hurry up, bro.

08:16.320 --> 08:18.680
Ruirui and I just went to buy you some food.

08:20.760 --> 08:21.520
Thanks.

08:22.520 --> 08:24.780
You guys talk. I'll go get some fresh air.

08:26.400 --> 08:27.680
If you need to pee again,

08:27.680 --> 08:28.740
call me to help you.

08:35.320 --> 08:37.440
You can help with that?

08:40.400 --> 08:42.039
His arm is in a cast.

08:42.440 --> 08:44.039
It's hard for him to use the bathroom.

08:44.039 --> 08:46.000
You... You helped him?

08:46.200 --> 08:47.680
Who else? Will you?

08:48.080 --> 08:50.360
No, no, no. You do it.

08:53.800 --> 08:55.130
Stop imagining things.

08:56.800 --> 08:58.720
No, no, no. I'm not.

08:59.520 --> 09:00.920
Do you want me to push you?

09:01.440 --> 09:02.160
No, thanks.

09:19.160 --> 09:19.880
Yuanbao.

09:20.880 --> 09:22.320
I know this incident

09:23.200 --> 09:26.200
has brought great physical and psychological trauma

09:26.440 --> 09:27.900
to both you and Mu Qingyun.

09:29.040 --> 09:30.280
As your teacher,

09:31.360 --> 09:32.690
I failed to protect you.

09:33.360 --> 09:34.040
I'm sorry.

09:34.960 --> 09:35.720
Similarly,

09:36.440 --> 09:37.800
as Gu Xinrui's teacher,

09:38.120 --> 09:39.720
I failed to educate her well.

09:40.240 --> 09:41.640
I also feel very ashamed.

09:41.880 --> 09:44.440
Mr. Tian, how can you be blamed for this?

09:45.120 --> 09:48.960
Instead, I often cause trouble

09:49.320 --> 09:50.560
and make you worry.

09:50.800 --> 09:52.130
Regarding this matter,

09:52.760 --> 09:54.290
I won't give you any advice.

09:54.640 --> 09:56.760
Whether you choose to settle or not

09:57.720 --> 09:59.780
is entirely up to you and your family.

10:05.240 --> 10:06.240
But that day,

10:07.000 --> 10:08.000
I received this.

10:08.920 --> 10:11.050
I wasn't supposed to show it to you now.

10:11.320 --> 10:12.560
But after seeing it,

10:13.200 --> 10:14.730
I took the liberty to decide

10:14.840 --> 10:17.240
that it's better to let you know in advance.

10:38.960 --> 10:41.000
Hello. I'd like to ask,

10:41.120 --> 10:42.000
are these lucky stars

10:42.000 --> 10:43.200
for making wishes?

10:43.320 --> 10:45.000
Yes, they are new arrivals.

10:45.120 --> 10:46.120
We have luminous ones

10:46.120 --> 10:47.120
and regular ones.

10:47.280 --> 10:48.960
There are many patterns to choose from,

10:48.960 --> 10:51.240
like zodiac signs, horoscopes,

10:51.320 --> 10:52.480
blood types, anime...

10:52.480 --> 10:53.400
We have all kinds.

10:53.400 --> 10:54.320
Which one do you want?

10:54.320 --> 10:55.780
I can open it for you to see.

10:56.600 --> 10:58.730
How many do I need to fold to make a wish?

10:58.760 --> 11:00.440
Different amounts have different meanings.

11:00.440 --> 11:02.300
It's explained in detail inside.

11:06.360 --> 11:07.620
Look at this question.

11:07.680 --> 11:09.080
It has options A and B.

11:09.440 --> 11:12.440
Then it's making a sentence with 'because',

11:13.120 --> 11:13.800
so...

11:20.880 --> 11:21.680
Are you tired?

11:22.400 --> 11:24.640
Let's call it a day.

11:25.880 --> 11:27.280
Not tired.

11:29.360 --> 11:31.960
Usually when you hear about tutoring,

11:32.480 --> 11:33.760
doesn't it give you a headache?

11:33.760 --> 11:34.800
Why are you so well-behaved today?

11:34.800 --> 11:35.530
No headache?

11:37.160 --> 11:38.290
No, it doesn't hurt.

11:38.480 --> 11:39.840
Because you explained it well,

11:39.840 --> 11:41.570
so I was completely engrossed.

11:41.600 --> 11:42.320
Really?

11:42.800 --> 11:44.040
Then tell me,

11:44.160 --> 11:45.240
where was I?

11:48.920 --> 11:49.780
This question.

11:50.440 --> 11:52.600
I talked about this question ages ago.

11:52.920 --> 11:54.480
You weren't engrossed.

11:54.560 --> 11:56.320
I think you were zoning out.

12:01.600 --> 12:02.680
By the way, Mutou,

12:03.360 --> 12:06.160
do you think going to juvie

12:06.240 --> 12:08.240
is a terrifying thing?

12:08.960 --> 12:10.490
Why ask this all of a sudden?

12:11.720 --> 12:13.440
Nothing, just asking.

12:14.480 --> 12:18.360
Were Gu Xinrui and Brother Shui sentenced?

12:18.800 --> 12:21.120
Not yet. Not that fast.

12:22.680 --> 12:24.360
But...

13:16.000 --> 13:17.800
Here is the current situation.

13:18.080 --> 13:20.440
Xinrui only instigated them to intimidate Xiong Yuanbao,

13:20.440 --> 13:22.120
and did not ask them to hit anyone.

13:22.120 --> 13:24.440
Otherwise, the consequences would be very serious.

13:24.440 --> 13:26.360
Although she can be released on bail for now,

13:26.360 --> 13:27.720
we still need to

13:27.800 --> 13:29.840
negotiate with the victim's family later

13:29.840 --> 13:32.120
so that we might reduce the penalty.

13:32.440 --> 13:34.000
All right. I understand.

13:34.120 --> 13:35.000
Thank you for your hard work.

13:35.000 --> 13:37.000
Okay, Mr. Gu. I'll take my leave now.

13:42.200 --> 13:43.660
Do you know how much effort

13:43.680 --> 13:44.960
I put into this for you?

13:45.920 --> 13:47.520
I have done my utmost for you.

13:48.080 --> 13:48.960
Mom, I...

13:49.240 --> 13:50.640
I really know I was wrong.

13:51.480 --> 13:52.610
You are grown up now.

13:53.440 --> 13:55.240
You need to take responsibility for your actions.

13:55.240 --> 13:56.080
Tomorrow I will send someone

13:56.080 --> 13:58.720
to take you back to school to go through the withdrawal procedures.

13:58.720 --> 14:00.200
After this matter is resolved,

14:00.200 --> 14:01.240
you will go back to the UK.

14:01.240 --> 14:02.720
I don't want to see you ever again.

14:02.720 --> 14:03.280
Mom,

14:03.600 --> 14:04.600
what did you say?

14:05.520 --> 14:06.760
Mom, I was wrong.

14:06.960 --> 14:08.420
Please don't send me away.

14:08.440 --> 14:09.560
I won't dare do it again.

14:09.560 --> 14:10.680
I promise to be good.

14:10.680 --> 14:11.800
I swear, okay?

14:12.600 --> 14:14.400
I'm getting married next month.

14:19.240 --> 14:21.500
I gave you such a superior material life,

14:21.840 --> 14:23.700
but failed to enrich your spirit.

14:25.680 --> 14:27.080
Look at what you've done.

14:27.360 --> 14:28.890
You really embarrassed me.

14:29.160 --> 14:29.960
How could I...

14:30.440 --> 14:31.120
How could I have

14:31.120 --> 14:33.320
such a disappointing daughter like you?

14:33.320 --> 14:34.040
Forget it.

14:35.040 --> 14:36.440
You'll be eighteen soon.

14:36.880 --> 14:40.480
You'll have to take responsibility for your own life from now on.

14:40.880 --> 14:41.960
This kind of mess,

14:42.440 --> 14:43.320
I will only

14:44.040 --> 14:45.760
clean up for you this one time in my life.

14:45.760 --> 14:47.420
If you cause any more trouble,

14:47.800 --> 14:49.000
I won't care anymore.

14:49.800 --> 14:51.040
You take her home first.

14:51.040 --> 14:52.300
I have something to do.

14:52.920 --> 14:54.080
Watch yourself.

15:03.280 --> 15:04.080
Auntie.

15:05.600 --> 15:06.400
Yuanbao.

15:11.920 --> 15:14.120
Can we talk?

15:28.240 --> 15:29.080
Child.

15:29.760 --> 15:31.620
I really need to apologize to you.

15:32.120 --> 15:33.650
I know words aren't enough.

15:37.760 --> 15:39.090
How are you recovering?

15:39.640 --> 15:41.040
Is Mu Qingyun doing okay?

15:41.360 --> 15:42.360
I'm much better.

15:42.920 --> 15:44.200
But Mu Qingyun

15:44.400 --> 15:46.800
still needs to be observed in the hospital.

15:47.280 --> 15:49.010
I'm really sorry to both of you.

15:49.760 --> 15:51.360
I failed to raise my son well.

15:52.120 --> 15:53.480
Making you endure all this

15:53.480 --> 15:54.680
at such a young age.

15:55.880 --> 15:56.640
Auntie.

15:57.480 --> 15:58.800
I came to find you today

15:59.560 --> 16:02.120
because I actually have something to tell you.

16:02.120 --> 16:02.960
Go ahead.

16:14.560 --> 16:16.400
Yuanbao, Mu Qingjun.

16:17.840 --> 16:19.040
This is what Gu Xinrui

16:19.480 --> 16:21.280
asked the police to hand over to me.

16:21.280 --> 16:24.280
She wanted me to wait until she finished her punishment

16:24.280 --> 16:25.240
and left the city

16:25.320 --> 16:26.650
before giving it to you.

16:27.000 --> 16:28.120
But as a teacher,

16:29.840 --> 16:31.640
I was worried about the content,

16:31.800 --> 16:33.160
so I had to review it.

16:33.920 --> 16:35.520
There are two videos inside.

16:35.800 --> 16:37.960
One is for you and Mu Qingjun.

16:39.120 --> 16:40.120
Take a look.

16:43.080 --> 16:45.240
Yuanbao, Mu Qingyun.

16:47.960 --> 16:48.720
I'm sorry.

16:50.040 --> 16:50.760
I know that

16:51.560 --> 16:54.600
even if I say I'm sorry a thousand times,

16:56.160 --> 16:58.320
it won't make up for my mistakes.

17:00.440 --> 17:01.320
I didn't...

17:01.880 --> 17:03.360
I didn't use to be like this.

17:03.360 --> 17:04.839
I don't know how I became

17:05.880 --> 17:06.839
so bad.

17:06.920 --> 17:07.599
So bad...

17:07.880 --> 17:10.680
So bad that I don't even recognize myself anymore.

17:10.839 --> 17:12.880
Jingu is my only friend.

17:14.800 --> 17:15.599
I admit

17:16.599 --> 17:17.359
I'm jealous.

17:18.480 --> 17:19.520
I'm jealous that he's close to you.

17:19.520 --> 17:21.520
I'm jealous that he treats you well.

17:22.800 --> 17:25.200
But I never thought of hurting you.

17:26.240 --> 17:27.720
I just hoped you would stay away from him

17:27.720 --> 17:29.160
and give him back to me.

17:29.600 --> 17:30.640
But this incident

17:30.800 --> 17:32.600
started because of me after all.

17:33.640 --> 17:34.480
I'm sorry.

17:34.520 --> 17:35.320
I really

17:36.400 --> 17:37.960
know I was wrong.

17:41.000 --> 17:42.040
Rest assured.

17:43.000 --> 17:45.130
No matter what crime I am charged with,

17:46.960 --> 17:47.960
I will accept it.

17:49.080 --> 17:51.720
I deserve it.

18:07.960 --> 18:08.880
I wish you

18:09.760 --> 18:10.960
a speedy recovery.

18:13.160 --> 18:14.420
And that you will never

18:15.200 --> 18:17.200
meet bad people again in your lives.

18:40.680 --> 18:41.940
There is another video

18:42.480 --> 18:43.810
she left for Meng Jingu.

18:44.160 --> 18:45.490
You should watch it too.

18:48.800 --> 18:49.560
Jingu,

18:50.400 --> 18:51.600
long time no see.

18:53.640 --> 18:54.480
I know

18:55.360 --> 18:56.960
my return from the UK

18:57.640 --> 18:59.400
has caused you a lot of trouble.

19:00.880 --> 19:02.560
I also know that this incident

19:05.720 --> 19:08.520
must have made you completely disappointed in me.

19:10.680 --> 19:11.520
I'm sorry.

19:13.840 --> 19:15.570
Actually, when I went to the UK,

19:16.120 --> 19:18.120
it wasn't just for further studies,

19:18.480 --> 19:19.200
but

19:19.400 --> 19:21.260
because my parents got divorced.

19:21.800 --> 19:23.400
I was given to my father in custody,

19:23.400 --> 19:26.600
so I went to the UK with him.

19:27.560 --> 19:29.420
Not long after arriving in the UK,

19:30.200 --> 19:31.440
I got a stepmother.

19:32.160 --> 19:35.360
After that, my life took a sharp turn for the worse.

19:36.280 --> 19:39.720
My stepmother is a very difficult person to get along with.

19:40.960 --> 19:41.640
One time,

19:42.360 --> 19:43.800
when my dad was away on a business trip,

19:43.800 --> 19:45.520
she actually pushed me down the stairs.

19:45.520 --> 19:47.980
I injured my waist and was almost paralyzed.

19:49.400 --> 19:51.000
I wanted to tell my dad about this,

19:51.000 --> 19:52.080
but he didn't believe me.

19:52.080 --> 19:53.800
Instead, he believed my stepmother,

19:53.800 --> 19:55.600
who said I got hurt from dancing.

19:55.760 --> 19:57.090
Later, in a fit of anger,

19:57.800 --> 19:59.400
I bought a plane ticket back.

19:59.600 --> 20:00.800
I originally thought

20:00.920 --> 20:02.980
about living with my mom in Shanghai.

20:03.000 --> 20:04.920
But I saw

20:05.360 --> 20:06.720
she had a new boyfriend.

20:10.480 --> 20:12.540
I became an unwanted presence again.

20:13.720 --> 20:14.680
I had no choice.

20:16.080 --> 20:18.610
I had to go back to my hometown in Jinghai City,

20:19.000 --> 20:20.560
and be taken care of by a nanny.

20:20.560 --> 20:21.680
I had no home,

20:22.600 --> 20:24.160
no love from my parents,

20:24.800 --> 20:25.880
and no dancing.

20:28.120 --> 20:29.080
I only have you.

20:33.440 --> 20:34.520
For so many years,

20:36.600 --> 20:38.260
you've been like family to me.

20:41.640 --> 20:42.440
Because

20:45.760 --> 20:47.280
I'm too afraid of losing.

20:47.400 --> 20:47.960
So.

20:50.280 --> 20:50.920
So.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.000
After reading it,

21:00.440 --> 21:02.240
I also feel very heavy-hearted.

21:03.320 --> 21:04.000
Yuanbao,

21:05.160 --> 21:06.280
I'll say it again.

21:06.840 --> 21:08.700
No matter what decision you make,

21:09.360 --> 21:10.440
I support you.

21:12.280 --> 21:14.840
You are both my students.

21:15.400 --> 21:16.200
I hope

21:17.600 --> 21:18.660
that in the future,

21:19.840 --> 21:22.040
you can both become pillars of society.

21:22.400 --> 21:23.160
Because.

21:24.320 --> 21:26.520
You still have a long road ahead in life.

21:35.600 --> 21:36.440
This child

21:37.440 --> 21:39.240
has suffered so much outside,

21:40.760 --> 21:42.600
and I knew nothing about it.

21:43.640 --> 21:45.040
She didn't even tell me.

21:46.840 --> 21:49.080
Why wouldn't she tell me?

21:49.920 --> 21:50.760
Auntie,

21:51.640 --> 21:54.360
I think for Gu Xinrui,

21:54.840 --> 21:56.370
what she wants isn't money,

21:56.600 --> 21:57.720
but your love.

21:59.160 --> 22:01.080
Because she lacks care so much,

22:01.840 --> 22:03.240
she would do

22:03.320 --> 22:04.800
such an extreme thing.

22:05.600 --> 22:06.720
I can't imagine

22:07.600 --> 22:08.560
if she lost

22:08.560 --> 22:10.520
her parents' company and care

22:11.320 --> 22:12.960
and her friends around her,

22:14.560 --> 22:15.360
even if

22:15.840 --> 22:18.040
she received the severest punishment,

22:19.200 --> 22:21.800
her future might not get better.

22:22.360 --> 22:23.760
What she needs is family.

22:26.040 --> 22:26.920
Auntie,

22:29.840 --> 22:31.280
we agree to settle.

22:36.680 --> 22:39.080
But our condition is

22:39.560 --> 22:41.080
that in the future,

22:41.680 --> 22:43.880
you must give her more company and care,

22:44.360 --> 22:45.480
educate her,

22:46.440 --> 22:48.760
and don't let her do wrong things again.

22:55.640 --> 22:58.440
Thank you, child.

22:59.960 --> 23:02.040
I really don't know what to say,

23:02.200 --> 23:03.860
and I have nothing to give you.

23:05.280 --> 23:07.610
This is a little token of my appreciation,

23:07.640 --> 23:09.770
and it's the only thing I can do for you.

23:10.440 --> 23:11.880
I hope you and Mu Qingjun

23:12.320 --> 23:13.480
recover soon.

23:17.120 --> 23:18.920
Auntie, no need for this.

23:19.840 --> 23:21.520
I appreciate your kindness.

23:22.560 --> 23:23.720
We agree to settle,

23:24.080 --> 23:25.360
and it's not for money.

23:25.640 --> 23:26.680
No matter what,

23:26.960 --> 23:28.690
Gu Xinrui is also my classmate.

23:28.840 --> 23:29.640
I know

23:30.240 --> 23:31.920
that me and Mu Qingjun getting beaten

23:31.920 --> 23:33.180
wasn't her intention.

23:33.320 --> 23:34.600
Those who hit us

23:35.040 --> 23:36.600
will be punished by law.

23:37.480 --> 23:38.680
As for Gu Xinrui,

23:39.960 --> 23:42.560
I want to give her a chance to turn over a new leaf

23:42.920 --> 23:44.450
and reduce her punishment.

23:46.040 --> 23:48.600
Child, you make me...

23:48.800 --> 23:49.560
Auntie,

23:50.160 --> 23:51.720
I've said all I want to say.

23:52.160 --> 23:53.120
I'll go first.

23:57.240 --> 23:57.920
Yuanbao.

24:11.600 --> 24:12.440
Thank you,

24:13.680 --> 24:15.240
and thanks to your family too.

24:15.240 --> 24:16.000
Auntie,

24:17.280 --> 24:19.040
please tell Gu Xinrui for me

24:20.280 --> 24:21.520
that we forgive her.

24:22.440 --> 24:23.120
Okay.

25:00.360 --> 25:01.040
Xinrui.

25:02.880 --> 25:04.280
I'm here to take you home.

25:05.680 --> 25:06.560
Home?

25:08.520 --> 25:09.520
Back to Shanghai?

25:12.400 --> 25:14.840
I... I think I should go back to the UK.

25:15.760 --> 25:17.820
I don't want to cause you any trouble.

25:20.880 --> 25:22.210
I canceled the wedding.

25:24.800 --> 25:25.640
Why?

25:29.720 --> 25:30.840
You silly child.

25:31.560 --> 25:32.800
You suffered so much.

25:33.120 --> 25:34.380
Why didn't you tell me?

25:37.320 --> 25:40.120
From now on, Mom will take care of you.

25:41.640 --> 25:42.570
Wherever Mom is,

25:43.120 --> 25:44.580
that's where your home is.

25:47.080 --> 25:48.120
Mom.

26:05.080 --> 26:07.360
How is he doing?

26:07.840 --> 26:10.300
The doctor said he's recovering quite well.

26:11.560 --> 26:12.880
My mom told me

26:13.640 --> 26:14.970
that you went to see her.

26:15.960 --> 26:16.680
Yuanbao.

26:17.440 --> 26:19.100
I didn't expect you to do that.

26:19.880 --> 26:21.080
In front of you guys,

26:23.960 --> 26:25.280
I feel truly ashamed.

26:27.680 --> 26:29.800
Thank you for waking me up.

26:33.240 --> 26:34.640
I was too extreme.

26:35.480 --> 26:37.740
If you had said things like this earlier,

26:38.160 --> 26:39.040
maybe

26:39.560 --> 26:41.760
we would already be good friends by now.

26:44.680 --> 26:45.600
I'm sorry.

26:48.320 --> 26:51.650
Do I still have the right to be friends with you in the future?

26:55.880 --> 26:56.680
Yes.

26:57.720 --> 26:59.640
Yuanbao, thank you.

27:01.480 --> 27:04.200
This matter is finally settled.

27:04.880 --> 27:08.210
The people who beat us were sentenced to two years in prison.

27:08.440 --> 27:10.700
Although Gu Xinrui got our forgiveness,

27:11.000 --> 27:13.600
she lost her student status as a result.

27:14.000 --> 27:15.840
She was also punished by the law.

27:16.200 --> 27:18.200
I heard she will follow her mother

27:18.200 --> 27:19.920
and move to a new city to live.

27:20.440 --> 27:23.440
I hope her future will also be bright.

27:31.680 --> 27:34.000
Silly girl, you are my sister,

27:34.360 --> 27:35.520
and my family.

27:35.960 --> 27:38.080
Family members should be honest with each other,

27:38.080 --> 27:39.010
shouldn't they?

27:39.560 --> 27:42.200
From now on, no matter what difficulties you face,

27:42.200 --> 27:43.460
or what's on your mind,

27:43.720 --> 27:45.280
you can tell your brother.

27:45.920 --> 27:46.760
With me here,

27:47.160 --> 27:48.400
you are not alone.

27:49.320 --> 27:50.760
Last time you went to the UK,

27:50.760 --> 27:52.090
you broke your promise.

27:52.600 --> 27:54.360
Now that you're back,

27:54.640 --> 27:56.640
you can't break your promise again.

27:56.720 --> 27:58.560
See you in college. Good luck.

28:23.640 --> 28:24.720
Xinrui.

28:27.480 --> 28:28.640
Xinrui.

28:28.800 --> 28:30.360
Welcome, Xinrui.

28:31.120 --> 28:32.600
Welcome, Xinrui.

28:32.720 --> 28:33.920
Xinrui, Xinrui.

28:33.960 --> 28:35.160
Welcome, Xinrui.

28:35.400 --> 28:37.880
Welcome, Xinrui.

28:45.560 --> 28:46.760
Thank you.

29:02.560 --> 29:05.800
I heard that when you fold 1,001 of them,

29:06.040 --> 29:07.760
your wishes will come true.

29:08.800 --> 29:11.160
I tried hard to forget the unhappy past,

29:11.640 --> 29:13.840
focus on my studies,

29:14.280 --> 29:15.740
and tutor Mutou every day.

29:15.800 --> 29:17.360
It has become

29:17.360 --> 29:19.360
the most anticipated part of my day.

29:36.640 --> 29:39.480
The language of baby's breath is silent protection.

29:39.480 --> 29:41.720
Mutou used to protect me silently.

29:42.520 --> 29:45.280
From now on, I will protect him.

29:50.240 --> 29:51.840
We couldn't keep our illness

29:52.160 --> 29:53.840
a secret from Grandma.

29:57.080 --> 29:58.000
Grandma, Grandma.

29:58.000 --> 29:59.600
I want to tell you something.

30:00.240 --> 30:02.840
But do you have your heart pills with you?

30:04.440 --> 30:05.560
Fortunately, Grandma

30:05.560 --> 30:07.400
is stronger than we thought.

30:08.000 --> 30:09.360
In the later stages of treatment,

30:09.360 --> 30:12.120
she went to the hospital to accompany Mutou every day,

30:12.120 --> 30:13.850
talking and laughing with him.

30:13.880 --> 30:15.360
Naturally, she and Grandpa Gong

30:15.360 --> 30:16.800
also met often.

30:27.880 --> 30:29.280
I heard Mutou say

30:29.440 --> 30:32.040
that Gong Yu got injured in the same spot twice,

30:32.480 --> 30:35.080
so it's very hard for him to fully recover.

30:36.080 --> 30:37.520
So his sports dream

30:37.640 --> 30:38.880
is shattered.

30:39.800 --> 30:42.330
And this ambitious boy wants to join the army.

30:42.760 --> 30:44.360
Maybe winning glory for the country

30:44.360 --> 30:46.480
is his eternal dream.

30:47.680 --> 30:48.520
I know

30:48.760 --> 30:50.290
that behind every smile...

30:50.600 --> 30:52.800
How much bitterness and fear is hidden?

30:53.760 --> 30:55.160
I should also think about

30:55.280 --> 30:57.280
my grandmother's own happiness.

31:00.640 --> 31:02.240
The day Mutou was discharged

31:02.360 --> 31:04.620
happened to be the first snow of the year.

31:04.720 --> 31:07.360
Grandma said a timely snow promises a good harvest.

31:07.360 --> 31:08.520
It's a good sign.

31:09.240 --> 31:12.200
If winter comes, can spring be far behind?

31:17.960 --> 31:19.800
Qingyun,

31:20.640 --> 31:21.520
Mutou.

31:21.680 --> 31:22.210
Alright.

31:22.240 --> 31:23.680
Quiet, everyone.

31:25.000 --> 31:27.480
Let's welcome Mu Qingyun and Gong Yu back to the team.

31:27.480 --> 31:28.240
Great.

31:28.800 --> 31:30.040
Welcome!

31:36.680 --> 31:37.360
Okay.

31:59.720 --> 32:02.280
Alpha, I'm glad you're safe.
